          <declname>iface</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Restart DHCPv6 client on an iface. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Restart DHCPv6 client on a given interface. DHCPv6 client will restart the state machine without any of the initial delays.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>iface</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>A valid pointer to a network interface </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
